[ ] Workflow
    [ ] Multi-select entities
    [ ] Copy/paste entities
    [ ] Grouping/parenting
    [ ] Search/filter entities
    [ ] Bookmarks/favorites

[ ] Project management
    [ ] Project settings window
    [ ] Build settings
    [ ] Quality presets
    [ ] Input configuration
    [ ] Tag/layer management

[ ] Debugging
    [ ] Frame debugger
    [ ] GPU profiler
    [ ] Memory profiler
    [ ] Physics debugger
    [ ] Draw call inspector

PHASE 8: EXPORT & DISTRIBUTION
------------------------------
[ ] Build pipeline
    [ ] Asset cooking/compression
