PRIORITY SHORTCUTS
==================
If building a specific game, skip:
- Terrain editor (if not open world)
- Networking (if single player)
- Advanced AI (if simple enemies)
- Material graph (use code instead)

Minimum viable engine for a 3D game:
- Rendering âœ“
- Animation
- Basic physics
- Simple scripting
- Scene save/load
- Audio
- Build export
